Installation:
=============

See the INSTALL file for details.


About:
======

This package contains various tools required to create game content
for the Adonthell Role Playing Game Engine. For related documentation
check the Adonthelli Documentation Wiki

    http://adonthell.berlios.de/doc/


Contact:
========

You can reach us in various ways:

Mailing list:  adonthell-general@nongnu.org
Web site:      http://adonthell.nongnu.org
Tech support:  http://savannah.nongnu.org/support/?group_id=702


Reporting Bugs:
===============

We hope you'll never have to, but if you discover a problem, we
would like to hear about it. Please use the Development mailing list
(adonthell-devel@nongnu.org) for that. You can
subscribe to the mailing lists at

    http://adonthell.nongnu.org/contact/mailinglist.shtml


Thank you for trying this software.
- The Adonthell team.
